Everybody knows about the big names. The celebrities. The A-listers. The masters of the box-office. But what about everyone else? There are hundreds of great films each year that only receive a limited theatrical run, and that's if they're lucky. It takes drive, determination and a lot of work to make a film, and not everyone who does it will make the cover of People magazine. &lt;br /&gt;
